{"tid":97211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投]接唔接受\"岩野黎架\"","createTime":"2017-01-27T13:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:25:59.000Z","uid":51229,"like":346,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b656f6d16a313eb693d0c65af0b8e6553042eec","tid":97211,"uid":51229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"連登同隔離登有文化差異<br />\n<br />\n隔離登不嬲淨係屌&quot;吾系甘牙&quot;, 因為係5p字，高登唔歡迎mk<br />\n<br />\n唔會屌&quot;岩野黎架&quot;等字，因為速成難打正字<br />\n<br />\n而家想搞個公投，睇下連登接唔接受岩野黎架，出左結果就唔該少數派收皮，唔好再屌，否則世界大戰到2046<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話&quot;岩&quot;同&quot;野黎架&quot;唔同，岩字完全唔啱音，但係我想投左個大方向先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: &quot;岩野黎架&quot;等難打既字可以接受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: &quot;岩野黎架&quot;等同5p字，不能接受"},{"pid":"b4b868cdde7a1d9e8a2f563fc532903934b2bb8b","tid":97211,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:12:55.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"c26474e94f2e988233c206bc65a9fa6fcb843c8c","tid":97211,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"o岩o野o黎o架"},{"pid":"4dbc44fd4d09ea8dcb0b21bb5cc377bb5567055a","tid":97211,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>o岩o野o黎o架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91df394a5f3041d74be00f7a2f0c7b5b8d81f76c","tid":97211,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>o岩o野o黎o架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿呆"},{"pid":"fad6ec464170aeec86b8fd1b3300dfc4ef80fc72","tid":97211,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"岩岩食左飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb1